## ğŸš€ Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Node.js (v14 or higher)
- npm or yarn

### Installation

1. Clone the repository**
```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/AITaskManager.git
cd AITaskManager
```

2. Install dependencies**
```bash
npm install
```

3. Install Tailwind CSS**
```bash
npm install -D tailwindcss
npx tailwindcss init
```

4. Start the development server**
```bash
npm start
```

5. **Open your browser**
Navigate to [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000)

## ğŸ¯ Usage Examples

This app intelligently parses natural language input:
````
Input: "Buy groceries tomorrow at 3pm"
- Category: Shopping
- Date: Tomorrow
- Time: 15:00
- Priority: Medium

Input: "Urgent: Submit project report Friday"
- Category: Work
- Date: Next Friday
- Priority: High

Input: "Doctor appointment next Monday morning"
- Category: Health
- Date: Next Monday
- Time: 09:00
- Priority: Medium

Input: "Gym workout every day"
- Category: Health
- Recurring: Daily
- Priority: Medium

Input: "Pay rent on 1/15"
-Category: Finance
- Date: January 15
- Priority: Medium
